{"article_id":"qBQhoVMBYedasCq7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Obama On Russian Hacking :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"'We Need To Take Action .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"And We Will '","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"President Obama says","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"the United States will respond to Russian cyberattacks","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the intelligence community has concluded","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"were part of an effort","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to influence the 2016 presidential election .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"In an interview with NPR 's Steve Inskeep","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that is airing Friday on Morning Edition ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"there is no doubt","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"when any foreign government tries to impact the integrity of our elections ...","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"we need to take action .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"And we will - at a time and place of our own choosing .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Some of it may be explicit and publicized ;","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"some of it may not be . ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Obama tells NPR","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"`` we will '' respond to Russian hacking","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"Listen · 0:29","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"0:29","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"U.S. intelligence officials have concluded","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"that hackers","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"working for Russia","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"hacked into the Democratic National Committee 's computer network , as well as the private email of John Podesta , a top adviser to Democratic presidential nominee Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Russia responded Friday morning .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Dmitri S. Peskov , the Kremlin 's spokesman , said","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"the U.S. needs to show some proof","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"or quit talking .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` It is necessary to either stop talking about it ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"or finally produce some evidence , ''","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"he told Interfax ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"per the New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` Otherwise , it all begins to look quite unseemly . ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"With the question of Russia 's ultimate motivation for the hack becoming increasingly divisive ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Obama was careful to not endorse a CIA assessment ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"reported by NPR and other news outlets ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that asserts","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that Russia 's goal was to elect Trump .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` There are still a whole range of assessments","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"taking place among the agencies , ''","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Obama told NPR ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"referring to an order","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"he has given","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"the U.S. intelligence community","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"to conduct a full review of the cyberattacks before Inauguration Day .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"`` And so","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"when I receive a final report ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"we 'll be able to ,","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"give us a comprehensive and best guess as to those motivations .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"But that does not in any way ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"detract from the basic point","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"that everyone during the election perceived accurately -","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"that in fact what the Russian hack had done was create more problems for the Clinton campaign","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"than it had for the Trump campaign . `` There 's no doubt","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"that it contributed to an atmosphere","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"in which the only focus for weeks at a time , months at a time were Hillary 's emails , the Clinton Foundation , political gossip","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"surrounding the DNC . ''","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"In fact , email had been a major focus","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"since before Clinton formally entered the presidential race ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"owing to revelations","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"first reported by the New York Times","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"that she used a private email server during her tenure","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"leading the State Department .","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Updates about the FBI 's investigation of the server dripped out at intervals throughout the entire campaign .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"The State Department also released Clinton emails at semi-regular intervals throughout the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"as did the conservative group Judicial Watch ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"which obtained them through a Freedom of Information Act lawsuit .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Obama did n't pin the blame for Clinton 's loss on the leaked information ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` Elections can always turn out differently .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"You never know","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"which factors are going to make a difference .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"But I have no doubt","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that it had some impact ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"just based on the coverage . ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Obama said","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"his goal is for a definitive White House report on the matter to be issued","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"before President-elect Donald Trump takes office on Jan. 20 .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"He was also careful to say","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"while the Russian hacks benefited Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"he is not suggesting","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Trump 's campaign helped coordinate the attacks","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"or played any role in them ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"other than to exploit them for political advantage .","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"`` They understood what everybody else understood ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"which was that this was not good for Hillary Clinton 's campaign , ''","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"the president said .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Obama acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that every `` big power '' spies and collects intelligence on each other ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"but ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"`` There 's a difference between that and the kind of malicious cyberattacks","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"that steal trade secrets","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"or engage in industrial espionage , something","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"that we 've seen the Chinese do .","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"And there is a difference between that and activating intelligence in a way","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"that 's designed to influence elections . ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Obama discussed cybersecurity with Vladimir Putin during a 90-minute meeting on the sidelines of the G-20 summit","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"held in China in early September .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"The president characterized the meeting at the time as `` candid , blunt , businesslike . ''","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"While Obama is threatening to retaliate against Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he has only about five weeks left in the Oval Office .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Trump has dismissed","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"- in fact , mocked -","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"intelligence assessments","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"tying the DNC and Podesta hacks to Russia ,","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"and he campaigned on improving the U.S. relationship with the country .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"In his interview with NPR , Obama appeared mystified by that stance .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"`` The irony of all this , of course , is that for most of my presidency , there 's been a pretty sizable wing of the Republican Party","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"that has consistently criticized me","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"for not being tough enough on Russia , ''","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"`` Some of those folks during the campaign endorsed Donald Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"despite the fact","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"that a central tenet of his foreign policy was we should n't be so tough on Russia .","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"And that kind of inconsistency","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"I think","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"makes it appear , at least ,","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"that their particular position on Russia on any given day depends on what 's politically expedient . ''","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"The president cited a recent Economist-YouGov poll","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that found","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"Republican voters view Putin much more favorably now","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"than they did before the 2016 presidential election .","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"`` This is somebody , the former head of the KGB ,","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"who is responsible","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"for crushing democracy in Russia ,","depth":17},{"id":134,"text":"muzzling the press ,","depth":18},{"id":135,"text":"throwing political dissidents in jail ,","depth":19},{"id":136,"text":"countering American efforts","depth":20},{"id":137,"text":"to expand freedom at every turn ;","depth":20},{"id":138,"text":"is currently making decisions","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"that 's leading to a slaughter in Syria .","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"And a big chunk of the Republican Party ,","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"which prided itself during the Reagan era and for decades","depth":17},{"id":142,"text":"that followed","depth":17},{"id":143,"text":"as being the bulwark against Russian influence ,","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"now suddenly is embracing him . ''","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"NPR reached out to the Trump transition team for comment","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"but has not received a response .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":149,"right":292,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":148,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":167,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":165,"right":166,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":154,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":3,"right":153,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":4,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":5,"right":151,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":6,"right":150,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":156,"right":163,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":160,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":157,"right":159,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":14,"right":158,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":15,"right":16,